Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你終於看這邊了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:02:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望師兄你能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給桐山一個警示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小少爺那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想起他說的話真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\fad(2000,0)\pos(176,298)}耀眼之暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被他催促著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後看著棋盤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就恢復了狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法繼續下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棋面就是這麼糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先感受到衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後感受到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和暴風雨一樣的 羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我怎麼看這個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和這種類型的人對局時間會很長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅長吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼叫「這種人」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能慌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被他抓住機會的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以為自己是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說著不能慌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底看錯了多少個等級啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想著要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想等著別人失誤的棋士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心裡隨意計算別人的等級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能在這裡倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都看不穿別人的棋力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己內心充滿私怨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把A級棋士當成雜魚對待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑的 耀眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他輕輕地咳嗽了一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道是在對我說「冷靜下來」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續被他催促著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用混亂的頭腦拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找著下一步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我蔑視他的事也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今我注意到這點而感到驚慌也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人全部 全部看穿了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜靜地坐在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在這裡因為羞恥而半途逃走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是真正的恣意妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中僅存的一點決心 繼續對局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 沒有任何懸念 對局結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 開始分析戰局
